  "summary": "Malicious code in wao (npm)",
  "details": "Wao@0.41.2 is a trojanized version of the legitimate wao CLI (an Arweave AO computer tool). The preinstall hook executes a 976KB ELF binary (disguised as src/deps.ts) that delivers a Shai-Hulud supply-chain worm payload at install time. The package depends on arjson and hbsig, which are companion malware packages from the same campaign. The worm executes a native binary during npm install with full system access. The publisher has deprecated this version and advises upgrading.",
